abstract: >
  A taxonomy-driven benchmark of 1,500 synthetic, labeled examples of AI agent
  and LLM failures, spanning 5 task domains (Coding, Mathematics, RAG/QA,
  Planning, Customer Support) and 12 root-cause failure categories
  (e.g. Hallucination, Reasoning Failure, Tool Use Failure, Safety & Alignment
  Failure), with severity ratings and rationale annotations.
